
Hey, this is going to be all things Fabric for getting Fanonic.net servers up-and-running.

- south tasks

- db tasks: create db + permissions, dump database, restore database

- nginx tasks: restart, put into maintenance mode

- puppet tasks: push puppet config to host and apply puppet

- web tasks: push static content, push source code, fetch uploaded media to local system, check that web server is up

- search index tasks: rebuild/update index

- Prompt the user to enter random words to prevent doing something stupid

- notification tasks: SNS, email, etc

- misc: happy, sad
